import merge from 'webpack-merge'

import baseConfig from './webpack/base'
import devConfig from './webpack/dev'
import prodConfig from './webpack/prod'
import { isRelease } from './webpack/utils/env'

export default () =>
  isRelease ? merge(baseConfig, prodConfig) : merge(baseConfig, devConfig)

import { join } from 'path'

export const mode = process.env.NODE_ENV ?? 'release'
export const isDevServer = process.env.WEBPACK_IS_DEV_SERVER === 'true'
export const isRelease = mode === 'release'
export const isDev = !isRelease // staging 포함
export const isDevNotTest = isDev && mode !== 'test' // for jest
export const rootDir = join(__dirname, '../../')
export const defaultPort = 3000

import { join } from 'path'

export const isRelease = mode === 'release'
export const isDev = !isRelease // staging 포함
export const isDevNotTest = isDev && mode !== 'test' // for jest
export const rootDir = join(__dirname, '../../')
export const defaultPort = 3000

import ReactRefreshWebpackPlugin from '@pmmmwh/react-refresh-webpack-plugin'

import { devServer } from './config/devServer'
import { isDevNotTest } from './utils/env'

export default {
  devtool: 'cheap-module-source-map',
  plugins: [isDevNotTest && new ReactRefreshWebpackPlugin()].filter(Boolean),
  devServer
}
